do list.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.fastsecurecontactform.com/"><strong>Fast Secure Contact Form</strong></a> lets your visitors send you a quick e-mail message and blocks all common spammer tactics. Additionally, the plugin has a multi-form feature, optional extra fields, and an option to redirect visitors to any URL after the message is sent.</p>\n<p><a href="http://www.faktor.cc/Fotomobil/wp-osm-plugin"><strong>OSM</strong></a> displays maps in your WordPress blog using the OpenLayers technology.</p>\n<p><a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/widget-logic-visual/"><strong>Widget Logic Visual</strong></a> lets you control on which pages widgets appear using conditional tags.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/qjUAevaUXwA" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 14:00:44 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"James";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:19;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:13:"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"WPTavern: Absolute Privacy Plugin Back In The Repository";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"http://www.wptavern.com/?p=6344";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:108:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/mgsavUgVDqU/absolute-privacy-plugin-back-in-the-repository";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1328:"<p>A few days ago, <a href="http://blog.sucuri.net/2012/02/vulnerability-in-the-absolute-privacy-plugin.html">Sucuri mentioned</a> that the Absolute Privacy plugin for WordPress contained a security vulnerability that would allow the ability to bypass the authentication mechanism and gain admin access to the application, that being WordPress. The plugin was subsequently pulled from the repository as there had not been any updates to fix the security issue for well over a year. Today however, the plugin can be found within the <a href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/absolute-privacy/">repository again</a> as the security issue has now been fixed. </p>\n<p>Related posts:<ol>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/absolute-privacy-plugin-now-at-v1-2" rel="bookmark" title="Absolute Privacy Plugin Now At v1.2">Absolute Privacy Plugin Now At v1.2</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/plugin-code-repository-bookmarklet" rel="bookmark" title="Plugin Code Repository Bookmarklet">Plugin Code Repository Bookmarklet</a></li>\n<li><a href="http://www.wptavern.com/plugin-repository-now-supports-videos" rel="bookmark" title="Plugin Repository Now Supports Videos">Plugin Repository Now Supports Videos</a></li>\n</ol></p><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~4/mgsavUgVDqU" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 14:00:04 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Jeffro";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:20;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:13:"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"Weblog Tools Collection: Printed WordPress Magazine Shipping First Issue";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/?p=11089";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~3/kJWYGBzMTUI/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1200:"<p>We had <a href="http://weblogtoolscollection.com/archives/2012/02/08/printed-wordpress-magazine-to-be-released-shortly/">previously mentioned</a> the first printing of <a href="http://wpcandy.com/quarterly">WPCandy Quarterly</a>, a <a href="http://wordpress.org/">WordPress</a> related quarterly print magazine from the folks at <a href="http://wpcandy.com/">WPCandy</a>, and now it looks like <a href="http://wpcandy.com/announces/quarterly-issue-one-ships">the first issue has begun shipping</a> to folks who had pre-ordered it.</p>\n<p>This is quite possibly the first ever printed WordPress publication, at least I can&#8217;t find any others, so this is a rather monumental occasion. It sounds like there are plenty left after pre-orders, so you should still be able to order one if you missed out.</p>\n<p>The images in the shipment announcement post look great, so if you have received your copy, we&#8217;d love to hear what you think.</p>\n<p><strong>Update:</strong> To clarify, I meant that this is quite possibly the first ever printed WordPress <em>magazine</em> publication.</p>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/kJWYGBzMTUI" height="1" width="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sun, 26 Feb 2012 14:00:29 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"James";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:21;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:13:"\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:5:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:42:"WordPress.tv: Rebecca Haden: WordPress SEO";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27:"http://wordpress.tv/?p=9231";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"http://wordpress.tv/2012/02/25/rebecca-haden-wordpress-seo/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1796:"<div id="v-WornMn11-1" class="video-player">\n</div>\n<br />  <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/" /></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/godelicious/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/delicious/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/" /></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gofacebook/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/facebook/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/" /></a> <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gotwitter/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/twitter/wptv.wordpress.com/9231/" />